						               													<description>Description from the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Many areas around the ruins of Brimstone are overrun with hordes of demonic and Undead creatures, growing in strength before unleashing upon the defenseless settlements across the countryside. To hold this gathering Darkness at bay, devout Heroes set out on Holy Expeditions to smite these blasphemous foes before they can spread their foul corruption throughout the land.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This 15-card Game Supplement for Shadows of Brimstone allows Hero Posses that include at least one Holy Hero to make any Adventure into a Holy Expedition! Including a new Adventure Card for Holy Expeditions, a set of new Encounters themed for these dangerous missions to smite Demonic and Undead foes, and a new Corrupted Enemy Trait card to make any Enemies you face off against possessed by demons, this set also introduces 8 all new Blessing and Judgement Sermons for use with the Preacher Hero Class.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;CONTENTS&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Card #512 Holy Vision (Preacher Sermon (Blessing))&amp;#10;     Card #513 Consecrate (Preacher Sermon (Blessing))&amp;#10;     Card #514 Fortitude (Preacher Sermon (Blessing))&amp;#10;     Card #515 Guide (Preacher Sermon (Blessing))&amp;#10;     Card #516 Ruin (Preacher Sermon (Judgement))&amp;#10;     Card #517 Wrath (Preacher Sermon (Judgement))&amp;#10;     Card #518 Voice of Command (Preacher Sermon (Judgement))&amp;#10;     Card #519 Exorcism (Preacher Sermon (Judgement))&amp;#10;     Card #520 Holy Expedition (Adventure)&amp;#10;     Card #521 Corrupted (Enemy Trait)&amp;#10;     Card #522 Gruesome Display (Mine Encounter)&amp;#10;     Card #523 Servants of Darkness (Mine Encounter)&amp;#10;     Card #524 Blasphemous Markings (Mine Encounter)&amp;#10;     Card #525 Confronting Evil (Mine Encounter)&amp;#10;     Card #526 Guiding Light (Mine Encounter)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
